Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.23,0:17:21.50,720p raw eng,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了守护我们的盟军！我们的朋友！\N{\fs48}to protect our allies, our friends,{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.50,0:17:24.80,720p raw eng,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了让所有的宝石从母星的暴政中获得自由！\N{\fs48}to free all Gems from Homeworld's tyranny!{\r}
