Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.83,0:17:59.00,720p raw eng,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是你对吧，玫瑰？\N{\fs48}It is you, isn't it, Rose?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.00,0:18:01.57,720p raw eng,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你-你到底在说什么？\N{\fs48}Wha-What are you talking about?{\r}
